          "text": "The spacecraft is 2.6 kilometers away so we are starting the mission.  We are not close enought he guard so I don't need to avoid it in this state of the mission. My velocity is 7.2 m/s which can be incremented and I cannot spot the prograde nor the retrograde. I will increase forward throttle to find the prograde.\n\n"
